&lt;li&gt;Folder transfer support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Better verification UX (maybe QR codes?)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;macOS build&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you have thoughts on what matters most ‚Äî I'd love to hear it.&lt;/p&gt;

