&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;Profile&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;userId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="dl"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;12345&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="dl"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="sr"&gt;/div&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="p"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;p&gt;With Server Components, only the necessary HTML is sent to the client, while the logic remains on the server.&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;h2&gt;


&lt;strong&gt;4. Improved Hydration&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;React 19 introduces enhancements to hydration, the process of making server-rendered HTML interactive. The new hydration mechanism is more efficient, ensuring faster interactivity for users.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


&lt;strong&gt;Highlights:&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Partial hydration: Only hydrate the necessary parts of the page.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Better handling of streaming data from the server.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Improved support for Suspense during hydration.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;




&lt;h2&gt;


&lt;strong&gt;5. Enhanced Context API&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;React 19 includes optimisations for the Context API, addressing common performance issues. Context updates are now more efficient, reducing unnecessary renders.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example: Using the Updated Context API&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight javascript"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="kd"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;ThemeContext&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;createContext&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="dl"&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s1"&gt;light&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="dl"&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;

