&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://tailwindcss.com" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Tailwind CSS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì Utility-first CSS, not actually a component library.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://vuejs.org" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Vue.js&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì Entirely different framework.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://angular.dev/" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Angular&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì Not React, full monolithic framework.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://svelte.dev" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Svelte&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì Competing framework.&lt;/li&gt;
